      <title>Boohoo 融资 3900 万英镑，呼吁投资者避开 Mike Ashley</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/boohoo-raises-39-million-urges-investors-to-shun-mike-ashley</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Boohoo Group Plc 筹集了 3930 万英镑（4980 万美元），试图帮助扭转陷入困境的业务，同时敦促投资者拒绝亿万富翁迈克·阿什利（Mike Ashley）加入董事会的要求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/boohoo-raises-39-million-urges-investors-to-shun-mike-ashley</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 08:44:14 GMT</pubDate>
